75
00:18:14,100 --> 00:18:16,100
That's OK.

76
00:18:16,100 --> 00:18:20,100
You understand?

77
00:18:20,100 --> 00:18:22,100
Let me tell you something, Robbie.

78
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:30,100
Something that might be surprising to you.

79
00:18:30,100 --> 00:18:32,100
What? Tell me.

80
00:18:32,100 --> 00:18:40,100
Well, Grandpa wanted me to study engineering, like him.

81
00:18:40,100 --> 00:18:45,100
Well, I wasn't clear about my future,

82
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:51,100
