83
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:54,100
What did you tell Grandpa?

84
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:56,100
The truth.

85
00:18:56,100 --> 00:19:00,100
Then you're not upset

86
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:02,100
